<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- include system scripts, page meta, and header code injection -->
    {squarespace-headers}
  </head>
  <body id="{squarespace.page-id}" class="{squarespace.page-classes}">

    <div class="site-container">

      <header class="site-header">
        <!-- site navigation -->
        <squarespace:navigation navigationId="siteNav" template="site-navigation" />

      </header>
      <div class="about-intro-section">
        <h1 class="page-header"> we dare you to believe in a better world—a world where empowering ideas drive positive change,
        heal communities, and foster a culture that cares.
        </h1>
        <p>
        driven by our core values of <b>curiosity</b>, <b>boldness</b> and <b>originality</b>, meets
        <b>compassion</b>, <b>integrity</b> and <b>sustainability</b>, we strive to create and empower ventures across
        industries that embody these principles
        and reflect our vision of a better world.
        <br>our mission is to make a lasting impact that resonates for generations to come.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class ="about-founders-section">
        <h2 class="page-subheader"> meet the founders <h2>
        <p>their unique blend of sensitivity and creativity, both logical and analytical, allows them to
        see the unseen.</p>
        <p>
        with their diverse backgrounds and lived experiences, michael kleynhans and carolyne wamono's shared passion for
        business, innovation, design, and technology came together to establish kuwona studios in 2022.<br><br>

        further united by their love for humanity, they aim to cultivate collaborations and true partnerships with like-minded
        individuals to create ventures that ultimately lead to a lasting, positive impact in the world.
        harnessing their expertise, michael and carolyne are dedicated to shaping businesses that resonate with the
        ever-evolving needs of the present and future.<br><br>

        with a hands-on approach, they strive for excellence, deeply involving themselves in every venture from start to
        finish to ensure its success.<br><br>

        if you're inspired by our vision and would like to learn more, we'd love to hear from you.
        reach out to us at <a href="/contact" class="explore-link"> office@kuwonastudios.com </a>
      </div>
      <!--Footer with open block field -->
      <footer class="site-footer">
          <hr class="horizontal-line">
          <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="newsletter">
              <h3 class=footer-header>subscribe to our newsletter for insights</h3>
              <form class="footer-form">
                <input type="text" placeholder="name" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="email" required>
                <button type="submit">→</button>
              </form>
            </div>
            <div class="follow">
              <h3 class=footer-header>follow</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>instagram</li>
                <li>x</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="legal">
              <h3 class=footer-header>legal</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>privacy policy</li>
                <li>terms & conditions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      © kuwona studios 2024
    </div>
  </div>
        <squarespace:block-field id="footerBlocks" columns="12" />
      </footer>

    </div>

    <!-- combo and minify scripts when not logged in -->
    <squarespace:script src="site.js" combo="{.if authenticatedAccount}false{.or}true{.end}" />

    <!-- other scripts, and footer code injection -->
    {squarespace-footers}

  </body>
</html>
